ermodynamics; Pettersen, I.H., Williams, G., Overhead projector doubles as a classroom 'rainbow machine' (2004) Phys. Educ., 39, p. 463; Bartels, R.A., Do dark objects really cool faster? (1990) Am. J. Phys., 58, pp. 244-248; Besson, U., Paradoxes of thermal radiation (2009) Eur. J. Phys., 30, pp. 995-1007; Knox, R.S., Physical aspects of the greenhouse effect and global warming (1999) Am. J. Phys., 67, pp. 1227-1238","Besson, U.; Department of Physics A Volta, University of Pavia, Via A Bassi 6, 27100 Pavia, Italy; email: ugo.besson@unipv.it",,,,,,,,01430807,,EJPHD,,"English","Eur. J. Phys.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-77649218354
